title: Carl Barks - Raw scans - Jippes
description:
Here's some raw scans specially made for tpb user kaarma33.

7 Barks inspired stories; all drawn by Daan Jippes except one by Vicar. Swedish text.
(The Vicar scan is from an old soiled and yellowed '70 publication. A nice & ugly example of bad printing technique: e.g. sloppy painted, wrong colors (purple roofs, pink skies, dark blue trees, yellow grass...), and all colors totally misprinted) :-)
